I ordered a luggage set to my new address, but I realized I have another order that was sent to my old address on the same street. I want to change the delivery address for that order to my new home. Also, I want to update my user default address to the new home as well. Lastly, I would like to exchange my tablet for the cheapest one available due to moving costs. Could you assist me with these requests? I prefer not to disclose my address details, but you should be able to look them up in my orders.
